        <Parent_String>food cupboards (general cupboards) [300249925], cupboards (case furniture) [300039183], case furniture [300038860], storage and display furniture [300164528], furniture by form or function [300048628], furniture [300037680], furnishings by form or function [300037342], furnishings (works) [300037336], Furnishings (hierarchy name) [300037335], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
